<item>
            <title>[SPR-2076] Add MessageSource support to HTML taglib</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-2076</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It would be nice if the HTML tags would contain support for message code resolving for the title, alt, accessKey and itemLabel attributes (just like the Struts HTML taglib).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I suggest adding titleCode, altCode, accessKeyCode and itemLabelCode attributes to specify a message code instead of a value.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
